显然没有明确的法律依据，不能随意认定为违法产品。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 26px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;“</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">水货一般被归在</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">‘</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">非授权正规渠道商品</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">’</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">，但尾单则不一定，多数的</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">‘</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">授权经销合同</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">’</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">一般会对尾单作出约定，如尾单回收、准许期满后一定时期销售或者尾单禁止出售等，所以对尾单不能一概而论。</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">”</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">滕立章认为。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 26px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">张延来也表示，</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">“</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">非授权正规渠道</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; COLOR: #333333\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman\">”</span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333\">在法律上的理解应当是非经品牌所有人授权销售的商品，因此这个概念可以部分涵盖水货